81        private String getResource(String packageName, String resourceName) {
82                IWorkspaceRoot workspaceRoot = ResourcesPlugin.getWorkspace().getRoot();
83                IResource resource = workspaceRoot.findMember(new Path("/Formatter/" + packageName + "/" + resourceName));
84                assertNotNull("No resource found", resource);
85                return resource.getLocation().toOSString();

88        private String getZipEntryContents(String fileName, String zipEntryName) {
89                ZipFile zipFile = null;
90                BufferedInputStream inputStream  = null;
91                try {
92                        zipFile = new ZipFile(fileName);
93                        ZipEntry zipEntry = zipFile.getEntry(zipEntryName);
94                        inputStream = new BufferedInputStream(zipFile.getInputStream(zipEntry));
95                        return new String(org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.compiler.util.Util.getInputStreamAsCharArray(inputStream, -1, null));
96                } catch (IOException e) {
97                } finally {
98                        try {
99                                if (inputStream != null) {
100                                        inputStream.close();
101                                }
102                                if (zipFile != null) {
103                                        zipFile.close();
104                                }
105                        } catch (IOException e1) {
106                                // Do nothing
107                        }
108                }
109                return null;
110        }

116        private String runFormatter(CodeFormatter codeFormatter, String source, int kind, int indentationLevel, int offset, int length, String lineSeparator) {
117//                long time = System.currentTimeMillis();
118                TextEdit edit = codeFormatter.format(kind, source, offset, length, indentationLevel, lineSeparator);//$NON-NLS-1$
119//                System.out.println((System.currentTimeMillis() - time) + " ms");
120                if (edit == null) return null;
121//                System.out.println(edit.getChildrenSize() + " edits");
122                String result = org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.core.util.Util.editedString(source, edit);
123 
124                if (length == source.length()) {
125//                        time = System.currentTimeMillis();
126                        edit = codeFormatter.format(kind, result, 0, result.length(), indentationLevel, lineSeparator);//$NON-NLS-1$
127//                        System.out.println((System.currentTimeMillis() - time) + " ms");
128                        if (edit == null) return null;
129//                        assertEquals("Should not have edits", 0, edit.getChildren().length);
130                        final String result2 = org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.internal.core.util.Util.editedString(result, edit);
131                        if (!result.equals(result2)) {
132                                assertSourceEquals("Different reformatting", Util.convertToIndependantLineDelimiter(result), Util.convertToIndependantLineDelimiter(result2));
133                        }
134                }
135                return result;
136        }

141        public void setUpSuite() throws Exception {

144                if (description.isAutoBuilding()) {
145                        description.setAutoBuilding(false);
146                        getWorkspace().setDescription(description);
147                }
148                setUpJavaProject("Formatter"); //$NON-NLS-1$
149                if (DEBUG) {
150                        this.time = System.currentTimeMillis();
151                }
152        }

162                super.tearDown();
163        }

165        private String getIn(String compilationUnitName) {
166                assertNotNull(compilationUnitName);
167                int dotIndex = compilationUnitName.indexOf('.');
168                assertTrue(dotIndex != -1);
169                return compilationUnitName.substring(0, dotIndex) + IN + compilationUnitName.substring(dotIndex);
170        }
171        
172        private String getOut(String compilationUnitName) {
173                assertNotNull(compilationUnitName);
174                int dotIndex = compilationUnitName.indexOf('.');
175                assertTrue(dotIndex != -1);
176                return compilationUnitName.substring(0, dotIndex) + OUT + compilationUnitName.substring(dotIndex);
177        }

179        private void assertLineEquals(String actualContents, String originalSource, String expectedContents, boolean checkNull) {
180                if (actualContents == null) {
181                        assertTrue("actualContents is null", checkNull);
182                        assertEquals(expectedContents, originalSource);
183                        return;
184                }
185                assertSourceEquals("Different number of length", Util.convertToIndependantLineDelimiter(expectedContents), actualContents);
186        }

221        private void runTest(String input, String output, CodeFormatter codeFormatter, int kind, int indentationLevel, boolean checkNull, int offset, int length, String lineSeparator) {
222                String result;
223                if (length == -1) {
224                        result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, input, kind, indentationLevel, offset, input.length(), lineSeparator);
225                } else {
226                        result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, input, kind, indentationLevel, offset, length, lineSeparator);
227                }
228                assertLineEquals(result, input, output, checkNull);
229        }

231        private void runTest(String source, String expectedResult, CodeFormatter codeFormatter, int kind, int indentationLevel, boolean checkNull, int offset, int length) {
232                String result;
233                if (length == -1) {
234                        result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, source, kind, indentationLevel, offset, source.length(), null);
235                } else {
236                        result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, source, kind, indentationLevel, offset, length, null);
237                }
238                assertLineEquals(result, source, expectedResult, checkNull);
239        }

241        private void runTest(CodeFormatter codeFormatter, String packageName, String compilationUnitName, int kind, int indentationLevel, boolean checkNull, int offset, int length, String lineSeparator) {
242                try {
243                        IJavaScriptUnit sourceUnit = getCompilationUnit("Formatter" , "", packageName, getIn(compilationUnitName)); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
244                        String s = sourceUnit.getSource();
245                        assertNotNull(s);
246                        IJavaScriptUnit outputUnit = getCompilationUnit("Formatter" , "", packageName, getOut(compilationUnitName)); //$NON-NLS-1$ //$NON-NLS-2$
247                        assertNotNull(outputUnit);
248                        String result;
249                        if (length == -1) {
250                                result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, s, kind, indentationLevel, offset, s.length(), lineSeparator);
251                        } else {
252                                result = runFormatter(codeFormatter, s, kind, indentationLevel, offset, length, lineSeparator);
253                        }
254                        assertLineEquals(result, s, outputUnit.getSource(), checkNull);
255                } catch (JavaScriptModelException e) {
256                        e.printStackTrace();
257                        assertTrue(false);
258                }
259        }
260 
261        String getSource(ASTNode astNode, char[] source) {
262                String result = new String(CharOperation.subarray(source, astNode.getStartPosition() + 1, astNode.getStartPosition() + astNode.getLength() - 1));
263                if (result.endsWith("\\n")) {
264                        return result.substring(0, result.length() - 2) + LINE_SEPARATOR;
265                }
266                return result;
267        }
